data.description: 3 bed 2 Bath *FABULOUS RANCH*  with a FULL FINISHED BASEMENT.  Fantastic REHAB: New KITCHEN with quartz counters, WHITE MODERN cabinets, recessed LED lights, STAINLESS steel appliances, under counter lighting, PORCELAIN floors and GLASS back splash.  UPDATED 1ST FLOOR bathroom with PORCELAIN tiles HEATED FLOORS, new vanity with MARBLE counters, new faucets, lights and fixtures.  FULL BASEMENT with a NEW BUILT IN BAR with wrap around counters and cabinets.  Excellent open MEDIA room all finished with new CERAMIC floors.  FULL BATHROOM and large LAUNDRY and STORAGE ROOM as well.  House FRESHLY PAINTED with modern Pottery Barn colors.  Crown molding and recessed LED lights throughout.  Back YARD is made for entertaining.  FULLY FENCED with a new DECK and BRICK patio and a DOG RUN!!!  EXCELLENT LOCATION walking distance to WEST PARK.  Minutes to downtown DES PLAINES, Metra, shopping and expressway. "Floor plan and square footage on tour/3D tour"
